						               													<description>A Ultima Fortaleza (The Last Fortress) is a cooperative AND competitive game of intrigue, bluff and tower defense. It's a game where humans, elven and dwarven heroes are the enemy and you play in the role of the monster, protecting your race from extinction.&amp;#10;The Last Fortress is the first Brazilian big board game with hundreds of components, several game modes and a rich fantasy background brought to life from the creative mind of the designer Fabiano Saccol.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Tha game is subdivided in a serie of seasons. In each season the players select two actions (build, recruit, buy cards, etc). After performing the actions, the players can move your units and engage the enemy heros. At the end of each turn new heros are put in game and move against the fortress.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The players win if the fortress is not destroyed. Then, the player with the most Power wins the game. If the fortress is destroyed all players lose.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
